OL,6,FJust before Christmas, the Police
OL,7,FOmbudsman revealed a former PSNI
OL,8,Fofficer had been arrested for
OL,9,F"several, non-recent offences alleged
OL,10,Fto have been committed while he was on
OL,11,Fduty and a serving police officer''.
OL,13,FThey include misconduct in public
OL,14,Foffice and a number of serious sexual
OL,15,Foffences.
OL,17,FUTV has since uncovered more about the
OL,18,Finvestigation, triggered after someone
OL,19,Fcame forward.
