OL,6,FWe can also reveal why this officer
OL,7,Fquit his job.
OL,9,FIt is understood the former officer
OL,10,Ffaced an internal PSNI misconduct
OL,11,Fhearing a number of years ago. It is
OL,12,Fclaimed he had sent sexual images.
OL,14,FHe was later required to resign.
OL,16,FDeputy Chief Constable Bobby Singleton
OL,17,Fsaid the ombudsman's investigation was
OL,18,Fwelcomed and they were "fully
OL,19,Fcooperating" with it.
