OL,6,FPolicing Board member Nuala McAllister
OL,7,Ftold UTV she will be asking the chief
OL,8,Fconstable about the case at the next
OL,9,Fmeeting of the Policing Board in
OL,10,FFebruary - the first of the new year.
OL,12,FIn a statement, the Police Ombudsman
OL,13,Fsaid investigators arrested a former
OL,14,FPSNI officer on "suspicion of
OL,15,Fcommitting more than 10 non-recent
OL,16,Foffences, including a suspected rape,
OL,17,Fother sexual offences, and misconduct
OL,18,Fin public office.
